data.description: This charming three-bedroom, one-bath home nestled on just over two acres of serene land offers a tranquil retreat in Davidson County. With the updated bathroom and flooring throughout most of the house, it seamlessly blends modern comforts with countryside charm. Plus, its a convenient 15-minute commute to downtown Nashville ensures you can enjoy both city life and peaceful surroundings effortlessly.
